{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1346,"text":"(Arabic) I seek refuge in Allah from cursed Satan.\nIn the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":4999,"text":"(English) I was born\nin a middle class family."},{"time":8642,"text":"My father was five years old\nwhen he lost his father,"},{"time":13233,"text":"but by the time I was born,"},{"time":16336,"text":"he was already a businessman."},{"time":19320,"text":"But it didn't make a difference to him"},{"time":21772,"text":"if his children were going to be\na boy or a girl:"},{"time":24704,"text":"they were going to go to school."},{"time":26879,"text":"So I guess I was the lucky one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30482,"text":"My mother had 16 pregnancies."},{"time":33926,"text":"From 16 pregnancies, five of us are alive."},{"time":39418,"text":"You can imagine as a child\nwhat I went through."},{"time":44008,"text":"Day to day, I watched women"},{"time":46881,"text":"being carried to a graveyard,"},{"time":50151,"text":"or watched children going to a graveyard."},{"time":55555,"text":"At that time, when I\nfinished my high school,"},{"time":58603,"text":"I really wanted to be a doctor."},{"time":61371,"text":"I wanted to be a doctor\nto help women and children."},{"time":66053,"text":"So I completed my education,"},{"time":68522,"text":"but I wanted to go to university."},{"time":71290,"text":"Unfortunately, in my country,\nthere wasn't a dormitory for girls,"},{"time":76585,"text":"so I was accepted in medical school,\nbut I could not go there."},{"time":81606,"text":"So as a result, my father\nsent me to America."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86999,"text":"I came to America."},{"time":88932,"text":"I completed my education."},{"time":91355,"text":"While I was completing my education,"},{"time":93799,"text":"my country was invaded by Russia."},{"time":98299,"text":"And do you know that at the time\nI was completing my education,"},{"time":102406,"text":"I didn't know what was going on\nwith my family or with my country."},{"time":106454,"text":"There were months, years,\nI didn't know about it."},{"time":110358,"text":"My family was in a refugee camp."},{"time":114789,"text":"So as soon as I completed my education,"},{"time":118844,"text":"I brought my family to America."},{"time":121400,"text":"I wanted them to be safe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124046,"text":"But where was my heart?"},{"time":126110,"text":"My heart was in Afghanistan."},{"time":128522,"text":"Day after day,\nwhen I listened to the news,"},{"time":131800,"text":"when I followed what was\ngoing on with my country,"},{"time":134498,"text":"my heart was breaking up."},{"time":136442,"text":"I really wanted to go back to my country,"},{"time":139014,"text":"but at the same time I knew\nI could not go there,"},{"time":141807,"text":"because there was no place for me."},{"time":144577,"text":"I had a good job."},{"time":146371,"text":"I was a professor at a university."},{"time":148680,"text":"I earned good money."},{"time":150506,"text":"I had a good life."},{"time":152196,"text":"My family was here."},{"time":154007,"text":"I could live with them."},{"time":156022,"text":"But I wasn't happy."},{"time":157904,"text":"I wanted to go back home."},{"time":160000,"text":"So I went to the refugee camp."},{"time":162912,"text":"And when I went\nto the refugee camp in Pakistan,"},{"time":166126,"text":"there were 7.5 million refugees."},{"time":169745,"text":"7.5 million refugees."},{"time":172898,"text":"About 90 percent of them\nwere women and children."},{"time":177811,"text":"Most of the men have been killed\nor they were in war."},{"time":181850,"text":"And you know, in the refugee camp,"},{"time":184698,"text":"when I went day-to-day to do a survey,"},{"time":187674,"text":"I found things you never could imagine."},{"time":192174,"text":"I saw a widow with five to eight children"},{"time":194873,"text":"sitting there and weeping"},{"time":197435,"text":"and not knowing what to do."},{"time":199396,"text":"I saw a young woman\nhave no way to go anywhere,"},{"time":203070,"text":"no education, no entertainment,\nno place to even live."},{"time":208736,"text":"I saw young men that had lost\ntheir father and their home,"},{"time":213538,"text":"and they are supporting the family\nas a 10-to-12-year old boy --"},{"time":218455,"text":"being the head of the household,"},{"time":220169,"text":"trying to protect their sister\nand their mother and their children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224113,"text":"So it was a very devastating situation."},{"time":227176,"text":"My heart was beating for my people,"},{"time":230128,"text":"and I didn't know what to do."},{"time":232533,"text":"At that moment, we talk about momentum."},{"time":235636,"text":"At that moment, I felt,\nwhat can I do for these people?"},{"time":239801,"text":"How could I help these people?"},{"time":241628,"text":"I am one individual.\nWhat can I do for them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245205,"text":"But at that moment, I knew"},{"time":247872,"text":"that education changed my life."},{"time":250745,"text":"It transformed me. It gave me status."},{"time":254483,"text":"It gave me confidence.\nIt gave me a career."},{"time":258138,"text":"It helped me to support my family,"},{"time":260376,"text":"to bring my family to another country,"},{"time":262855,"text":"to be safe."},{"time":264853,"text":"And I knew that at that moment"},{"time":267614,"text":"that what I should give to my people\nis education and health,"},{"time":271932,"text":"and that's what I went after."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273942,"text":"But do you think it was easy?"},{"time":276695,"text":"No, because at that time, education\nwas banned for girls, completely."},{"time":284346,"text":"And also, by Russia invading Afghanistan,"},{"time":288058,"text":"people were not trusting anyone."},{"time":291058,"text":"It was very hard to come and say,\n\"I want to do this.\""},{"time":294804,"text":"Who am I?"},{"time":296249,"text":"Somebody who comes from the United States."},{"time":298399,"text":"Somebody who got educated here."},{"time":300321,"text":"Did they trust me? Of course not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303622,"text":"So I really needed to build\nthe trust in this community."},{"time":307960,"text":"How am I going to do that?"},{"time":310372,"text":"I went and surveyed and looked and looked."},{"time":313626,"text":"I asked."},{"time":314959,"text":"Finally, I found one man."},{"time":317674,"text":"He was 80 years old."},{"time":319412,"text":"He was a mullah."},{"time":321435,"text":"I went to his tent in the camp,"},{"time":324451,"text":"and I asked him,"},{"time":326070,"text":"\"I want to make you a teacher.\""},{"time":329117,"text":"And he looked at me,"},{"time":330792,"text":"and he said, \"Crazy woman,"},{"time":333157,"text":"crazy woman, how do you think\nI can be a teacher?\""},{"time":337911,"text":"And I told him,\n\"I will make you a teacher.\""},{"time":340705,"text":"Finally, he accepted my offer,"},{"time":343554,"text":"and once I started a class\nin his compound,"},{"time":346935,"text":"the word spread all over."},{"time":349657,"text":"In a matter of one year,"},{"time":351823,"text":"we had 25 schools set up,"},{"time":354768,"text":"15,000 children going to school,"},{"time":357736,"text":"and it was amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359856,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362117,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":364236,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366252,"text":"But of course, we're doing all our work,\nwe were giving teacher training."},{"time":371818,"text":"We were training women's rights,\nhuman rights, democracy, rule of law."},{"time":376611,"text":"We were giving all kinds of training."},{"time":379064,"text":"And one day, I tell you,"},{"time":382087,"text":"one day I was in the office\nin Peshawar, Pakistan."},{"time":386556,"text":"All of a sudden, I saw my staff\nrunning to rooms and locking the doors"},{"time":391490,"text":"and telling me, \"Run away, hide!\""},{"time":395268,"text":"And you know, as a leader, what do you do?"},{"time":398419,"text":"You're scared. You know it's dangerous."},{"time":402317,"text":"You know your life is on the line."},{"time":404111,"text":"But as a leader,\nyou have to hold it together."},{"time":407309,"text":"You have to hold it together\nand show strength."},{"time":410412,"text":"So I said, \"What's going on?\""},{"time":412642,"text":"And these people were pouring\ninto my office."},{"time":415880,"text":"So I invited them to the office."},{"time":417563,"text":"They came, and there were\nnine of them -- nine Taliban."},{"time":422753,"text":"They were the ugliest looking men\nyou can ever see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425499,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":427564,"text":"Very mean-looking people,"},{"time":429586,"text":"black clothes, black turban,"},{"time":431857,"text":"and they pour into my office."},{"time":434046,"text":"And I invited them\nto have a seat and have tea."},{"time":437641,"text":"They said no. They are not\ngoing to drink tea."},{"time":440934,"text":"And of course, with the tone\nof voice they were using,"},{"time":444410,"text":"it was very scary,"},{"time":445830,"text":"but I was really shaking up."},{"time":448441,"text":"But also I was strong, holding myself up."},{"time":452424,"text":"And, of course, by that time,\nyou know how I dress --"},{"time":455378,"text":"I dress from head to toe in a black hijab."},{"time":457973,"text":"The only thing you could see, my eyes."},{"time":461464,"text":"They asked me, \"What are you doing?"},{"time":463942,"text":"Don't you know that school\nis banned for girls?"},{"time":467776,"text":"What are you doing here?\""},{"time":469926,"text":"And you know, I just looked at them,"},{"time":472547,"text":"and I said, \"What school?\nWhere is the school?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":475507,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":478332,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":481452,"text":"And they look at my face, and they said,\n\"You are teaching girls here.\""},{"time":485237,"text":"I said, \"This is a house of somebody."},{"time":488428,"text":"We have some students coming,"},{"time":490356,"text":"and they are all learning\nKoran, Holy Book."},{"time":493792,"text":"And you know, Koran says that\nif you learn the Holy Book, the woman,"},{"time":498086,"text":"they can be a good wife,"},{"time":500363,"text":"and they can obey their husband.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":502768,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506936,"text":"And I tell you one thing:"},{"time":508777,"text":"that's the way you work with those people,\nand you know --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":511524,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512999,"text":"So by that time,\nthey started speaking Pashto."},{"time":517046,"text":"They talked to each other,"},{"time":518999,"text":"and they said, \"Let's go,\nleave her alone, she's OK.\""},{"time":522904,"text":"And you know, this time,\nI offered them tea again,"},{"time":526832,"text":"and they took a sip and they left."},{"time":530141,"text":"By that time, my staff\npoured into my office."},{"time":534292,"text":"They were scared to death."},{"time":536331,"text":"They didn't know why they didn't kill me."},{"time":538426,"text":"They didn't know why\nthey didn't take me away."},{"time":540887,"text":"But everybody was happy to see me."},{"time":544164,"text":"Very happy, and I was happy\nto be alive, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547181,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548356,"text":"Of course, I was happy to be alive."},{"time":550394,"text":"But also, as we continuously gave\ntraining during the fall of the Taliban --"},{"time":556294,"text":"of course during the Taliban\nthere is another story."},{"time":558755,"text":"We went underground and we provided\neducation for 80 schoolgirls,"},{"time":562938,"text":"3,000 students underground,\nand continuously we trained."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566802,"text":"With the fall of the Taliban,\nwe went into the country,"},{"time":569743,"text":"and we opened school after school."},{"time":572227,"text":"We opened women's learning center."},{"time":574656,"text":"We continuously opened clinics."},{"time":576616,"text":"We worked with mothers and children."},{"time":578624,"text":"We had reproductive health training."},{"time":580371,"text":"We had all kinds of training\nthat you can imagine."},{"time":583489,"text":"I was very happy. I was delighted\nwith the outcome of my work."},{"time":588155,"text":"And one day, with four trainers\nand one bodyguard,"},{"time":591771,"text":"I was going up north of Kabul,"},{"time":594692,"text":"and all of a sudden, again,"},{"time":597239,"text":"I was stopped in the middle of the road"},{"time":599541,"text":"by 19 young men."},{"time":601836,"text":"Rifles on their shoulders,\nthey blocked the road."},{"time":605646,"text":"And I told my driver, \"What's going on?\""},{"time":608575,"text":"And the driver said, \"I don't know.\""},{"time":610322,"text":"He asked them. They said,\n\"We have nothing to do with you.\""},{"time":613115,"text":"They called my name.\nThey said, \"We want her.\""},{"time":616828,"text":"My bodyguard got out, said,\n\"I can answer you."},{"time":619755,"text":"What do you want?\""},{"time":621073,"text":"They said, \"Nothing.\" They called my name."},{"time":623104,"text":"And by that time, the women\nare yelling and screaming inside the car."},{"time":627999,"text":"I am very shaken up,\nand I told myself, this is it."},{"time":630578,"text":"This time, we all are going to be killed."},{"time":633119,"text":"There is no doubt in my mind."},{"time":635721,"text":"But still, the moment comes,\nand you take strength"},{"time":640657,"text":"from whatever you believe\nand whatever you do."},{"time":643555,"text":"It's in your heart."},{"time":644944,"text":"You believe in your worth,\nand you can walk on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647843,"text":"So I just hold myself\non the side of the car."},{"time":651406,"text":"My leg was shaking, and I got outside."},{"time":654985,"text":"And I asked them, \"What can I do for you?\""},{"time":657509,"text":"You know what they said to me?"},{"time":659120,"text":"They said, \"We know who you are."},{"time":662286,"text":"We know where you are going."},{"time":664232,"text":"Every day you go up north here and there."},{"time":666937,"text":"You train women, you teach them"},{"time":670009,"text":"and also you give them an\nopportunity to have a job."},{"time":673080,"text":"You build their skills. How about us?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":675904,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":678779,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":681771,"text":"\"And you know, how about us?"},{"time":686159,"text":"What are we going to do?\""},{"time":687769,"text":"I looked at them, and I said,\n\"I don't know.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":690165,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":693007,"text":"They said, \"It's OK."},{"time":694602,"text":"The only thing we can do, what we know,"},{"time":696786,"text":"from the time we're born,\nwe just hold the gun and kill."},{"time":699889,"text":"That's all we know.\""},{"time":701713,"text":"And you know what that means."},{"time":703206,"text":"It's a trap to me, of course."},{"time":705522,"text":"So I walk out of there.\nThey said, \"We'll let you go, go.\""},{"time":709435,"text":"And so I walked into the car,\nI sit in the car,"},{"time":712363,"text":"and I told the driver,\n\"Turn around and go back to the office.\""},{"time":715999,"text":"At that time, we only\nwere supporting girls."},{"time":719436,"text":"We only had money for women to train them,"},{"time":722921,"text":"to send them to school, and nothing else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725881,"text":"By the time I came to the office,"},{"time":728722,"text":"of course my trainers were gone."},{"time":730999,"text":"They ran away home. Nobody stayed there."},{"time":734414,"text":"My bodyguard was the only one there,"},{"time":737390,"text":"and my voice was completely gone."},{"time":740120,"text":"I was shaken up, and I sat on my table,"},{"time":743279,"text":"and I said, \"What am I going to do?\""},{"time":745827,"text":"How am I going to solve this problem?"},{"time":748327,"text":"Because we had training\ngoing on up north already."},{"time":752080,"text":"Hundreds of women were there\ncoming to get training."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756295,"text":"So I was sitting there,\nall of a sudden, at this moment,"},{"time":760072,"text":"talking about momentum, we are,"},{"time":762501,"text":"at that moment,"},{"time":764406,"text":"one of my wonderful donors\ncalled me about a report."},{"time":769207,"text":"And she asked me, \"Sakena?\"\nAnd I answered her."},{"time":772764,"text":"She said, \"It's not you.\nWhat's wrong with you?\""},{"time":775136,"text":"I said, \"Nothing.\" I tried to cover."},{"time":778461,"text":"No matter what I tried to do,\nshe didn't believe me,"},{"time":781341,"text":"and she asked me again."},{"time":783016,"text":"\"OK, tell me what's going on?\""},{"time":784882,"text":"I told her the whole story."},{"time":786944,"text":"At that time, she said, \"OK,\nyou go next time, and you will help them."},{"time":792222,"text":"You will help them.\""},{"time":794142,"text":"And when, two days later,\nI went the same route,"},{"time":798364,"text":"and do you know, they were not in here,"},{"time":800881,"text":"they were a little back further,"},{"time":803078,"text":"the same young men, standing up there\nand holding the rifle"},{"time":807651,"text":"and pointing to us to stop the car."},{"time":809981,"text":"So we stopped the car."},{"time":811729,"text":"I got out. I said, \"OK, let's go with me.\""},{"time":814999,"text":"And they said, \"Yes.\""},{"time":816301,"text":"I said, \"On one condition,\nthat whatever I say, you accept it.\""},{"time":821046,"text":"And they said, yes, they do."},{"time":822649,"text":"So I took them to the mosque,"},{"time":824863,"text":"and to make a long story short,"},{"time":827999,"text":"I told them I'd give them teachers."},{"time":830763,"text":"Today, they are the best trainers."},{"time":834739,"text":"They learn English,"},{"time":836422,"text":"they learn how to be teachers,"},{"time":838882,"text":"they learn computers,"},{"time":840644,"text":"and they are my guides."},{"time":842518,"text":"Every area that is unknown to us\nin the mountain areas,"},{"time":846379,"text":"they go with me.\nThey are ahead, and we go."},{"time":848650,"text":"And they protect us."},{"time":851275,"text":"And --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":852450,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":853625,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854800,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":858330,"text":"That tells you that education\ntransforms people."},{"time":863513,"text":"When you educate people,"},{"time":865671,"text":"they are going to be different,"},{"time":867663,"text":"and today all over,"},{"time":869370,"text":"we need to work for gender equality."},{"time":871766,"text":"We cannot only train women\nbut forget about the men,"},{"time":875496,"text":"because the men are the real people\nwho are giving women the hardest time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880974,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":882577,"text":"So we started training men\nbecause the men should know"},{"time":886362,"text":"the potential of women,"},{"time":887853,"text":"know how much these potential men has,"},{"time":890378,"text":"and how much these women\ncan do the same job they are doing."},{"time":894997,"text":"So we are continuously giving\ntraining to men,"},{"time":898401,"text":"and I really believe strongly."},{"time":901711,"text":"I live in a country\nthat was a beautiful country."},{"time":904855,"text":"I just want to share this with you."},{"time":907006,"text":"It was a beautiful country,"},{"time":908848,"text":"beautiful, peaceful country."},{"time":911276,"text":"We were going everywhere."},{"time":913252,"text":"Women were getting education:"},{"time":915349,"text":"lawyer, engineer, teacher,"},{"time":918205,"text":"and we were going from house to house."},{"time":920396,"text":"We never locked our doors."},{"time":922912,"text":"But you know what happened to my country."},{"time":924898,"text":"Today, people cannot walk\nout of their door without security issues."},{"time":931297,"text":"But we want the same\nAfghanistan we had before."},{"time":936254,"text":"And I want to tell you the other side."},{"time":938222,"text":"Today, the women of Afghanistan\nare working very, very hard."},{"time":942166,"text":"They are earning degrees.\nThey are training to be lawyers."},{"time":946650,"text":"They are training to be\ndoctors, back again."},{"time":948904,"text":"They are training to be teachers,"},{"time":950578,"text":"and they are running businesses."},{"time":952927,"text":"So it is so wonderful"},{"time":955389,"text":"to see people like that\nreach their complete potential,"},{"time":960109,"text":"and all of this is going to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":962712,"text":"I want to share this with you,"},{"time":964578,"text":"because of love,"},{"time":966292,"text":"because of compassion,"},{"time":968109,"text":"and because of trust and honesty."},{"time":971220,"text":"If you have these few things with you,"},{"time":974939,"text":"you will accomplish."},{"time":977019,"text":"We have one poet, Mawlānā Rūmī."},{"time":980590,"text":"He said that by having compassion"},{"time":985424,"text":"and having love,\nyou can conquer the world."},{"time":988671,"text":"And I tell you, we could."},{"time":990265,"text":"And if we could do it in Afghanistan,"},{"time":992550,"text":"I am sure 100 percent that everyone\ncan do it in any part of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996916,"text":"Thank you very, very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":998679,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1001548,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006999,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}